== 机场设施 ==
努克机场拥有一个客运航站楼和一个格陵兰航空的作为其技术中心的货运航站楼。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://airgreenland.com/cargo/information_og_adresser/ |publisher=Air Greenland |title=Cargo Contact |accessdate=15 July 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081016092820/http://www.airgreenland.com/cargo/information_og_adresser/ |archivedate=2008年10月16日 }}</ref>机场配有[[测距仪|测距仪]]。
=== 航站楼 ===
[[File:Nuuk-airport-air-greenland-checkin-desk.jpg|thumb]]
努克机场的航站楼拥有三个登机口，它们位于值机柜台和候机大厅附近。行李转盘被单独装置于航站楼内。努克机场周日关闭。<ref name="AIP"/>
=== 地面交通 ===
诺普巴士（Nuup Bussii）三号线连接机场与努克Centrum区。巴士在每周一到周五的高峰期每小时从机场出发一班<ref>{{cite book|last=O'Carroll|first=Etain|title=Greenland and the Arctic|publisher=Lonely Planet|pages=153|year=2005|isbn=1-74059-095-3}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bus.gl/Køreplaner/tabid/56/Default.aspx |publisher=Nuup Bussii |title=Time Tables |accessdate=15 July 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321072137/http://www.bus.gl/K%C3%B8replaner/tabid/56/Default.aspx |archivedate=2012年3月21日 }}</ref>。由Nuna Taxa运营的出租车亦可供选择。.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://airgreenland.com/information/voresdestinationer/flybilletter_til_nuuk/ |publisher=Air Greenland |title=Nuuk |accessdate=15 July 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100617204446/http://www.airgreenland.com/information/voresdestinationer/flybilletter_til_nuuk/ |archivedate=2010年6月17日 }}</ref>有时限的私家车停车位位于航站楼外。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.knr.gl/index.php?id=297&tx_ttnews%5BpS%5D=1151719200&tx_ttnews%5BpL%5D=2678399&tx_ttnews%5Barc%5D=1&tx_ttnews%5Bpointer%5D=5&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=13965&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=844&cHash=bb6ca7b157 |title=Snart slut med langtidsparkering i Nuuk Lufthavn |work=[[Kalaallit_Nunaata_Radioa|Kalaallit Nunaata Radioa]] |language=da |date=13 July 2006 |accessdate=15 July 2010 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231213/http://knr.gl/index.php?id=297&tx_ttnews%5BpS%5D=1151719200&tx_ttnews%5BpL%5D=2678399&tx_ttnews%5Barc%5D=1&tx_ttnews%5Bpointer%5D=5&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=13965&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=844&cHash=bb6ca7b157 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
== 航空事故 ==
*1973年一架Grønlandsfly的[[SH-3海王直昇機|西科斯基S-61N直升机]]在努克以南40公里海域坠毁（可能由于螺旋桨停止工作），机上15人全部遇难。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aviation-safety.net/wikibase/wiki.php?id=33618 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-02-10 |archive-date=2014-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214105206/http://aviation-safety.net/wikibase/wiki.php?id=33618 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2008年6月一架格陵兰航空的[[歐直AS350松鼠一型直升機|松鼠一型直升机]]在努克机场跑道坠毁，<ref name="crash">{{cite news |url=http://sermitsiaq.ag/helikopter-styrtet-nuuk |title=Helikopter styrtet ned i Nuuk |work=[[Sermitsiaq_(newspaper)|Sermitsiaq]] |date=7 June 2008 |language=da |accessdate=6 July 2014 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726185053/https://sermitsiaq.ag/helikopter-styrtet-nuuk |dead-url=no }}</ref>无人受伤，但飞机本身严重损坏无法修复。<ref name="crash"/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://sermitsiaq.ag/spiritusrelaterede-opgaver-politiet-nuuk |title=Mange spiritusrelaterede opgaver for politiet i Nuuk |work=[[Sermitsiaq_(newspaper)|Sermitsiaq]] |date=9 June 2008 |language=da |accessdate=6 July 2014 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726185126/https://sermitsiaq.ag/spiritusrelaterede-opgaver-politiet-nuuk |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2011年3月，一架[[冰岛航空|冰岛航空]]的[[Dash_8|Dash 8]]在降落时起落架脱落，无人受伤，但是飞机严重损坏。

